FORMAT: 1A
HOST: http://localhost:3000

# Book Management API

API dùng để quản lý sách (CRUD, tìm kiếm, cập nhật...)

# Group Books

## Books Collection [/api/books]

### Get all books [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            [
              {
                "id": "1",
                "title": "Clean Code",
                "author": "Robert C. Martin",
                "price": 30
              }
            ]


### Create a new book [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Body

            {
              "id": "1",
              "title": "Clean Code",
              "author": "Robert C. Martin",
              "price": 30
            }

+ Response 201

    + Body

            {
              "message": "Book created"
            }


## Book Detail [/api/books/{id}]

+ Parameters

    + id: `1` (string, required) - ID của sách

---

### Get book by ID [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
              "id": "1",
              "title": "Clean Code",
              "author": "Robert C. Martin",
              "price": 30
            }

+ Response 404

    + Body

            {
              "message": "Book not found"
            }

---

### Update a book [PUT]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Body

            {
              "title": "Clean Code Updated",
              "author": "Robert C. Martin",
              "price": 35
            }

+ Response 200

    + Body

            {
              "message": "Book updated"
            }

+ Response 404

    + Body

            {
              "message": "Book not found"
            }

---

### Delete a book [DELETE]

+ Response 200

    + Body

            {
              "message": "Book deleted"
            }